{"tid":692942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九霄驚魂】冰雹打爛駕駛艙玻璃　美航客機急降　130名乘客幸無恙","createTime":"2018-06-07T05:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T09:01:35.000Z","uid":153228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dba8c3177ef781e6b1872ec7af6060960810781f","tid":692942,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180607/s00005/1528341506340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F1528341506340&d=R949l7d43WBU2XNm%2FySWvY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6f82fa5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F1528341506340&h=5dc1de27\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180607/s00005/1528341506340</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180607/s00005/72623fdac5418e985b211a155b82ef0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F72623fdac5418e985b211a155b82ef0d.jpg&h=43e0bf3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180607/s00005/7266a8c6ec7aef30afb699e957ae824b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F7266a8c6ec7aef30afb699e957ae824b.jpg&h=05b6755a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機頭被擊破穿了一個大洞(Twitter截圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180607/s00005/7269ec43edea3f09077dba51e79b4de6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F7269ec43edea3f09077dba51e79b4de6.jpg&h=06b714c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n駕駛艙玻璃碎裂，看不到窗外情況（Twitter截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國航空（American Airlines）一架客機飛行途中遇到惡劣天氣，冰雹打爛駕駛艙玻璃，機師幾乎看不到窗外情況最終迫降，幸好無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n美國航空編號AA1897的A319空中巴士客機載着130名乘客和5名機員，當地周日晚從得州聖安東尼奧出發前往亞利桑那州鳳凰城，飛行途中遭遇惡劣天氣，冰雹擊中駕駛艙擋風玻璃，令擋風玻璃破裂，機頭亦被擊穿，出現一個大洞。<br />\n<br />\n有乘客憶述當時見到窗外有閃電，亦清楚聽到冰雹打在機身的聲音，氣流令客機顛簸儼如坐過山車一般，乘客物品在機艙內橫飛，眾多乘客感到不適拿着嘔吐袋。<br />\n<br />\n由於駕駛艙擋風玻璃被冰雹打爛，機師最終將客機緊急降落在得州埃爾帕索的機場。美航指無人報稱受傷，數小時後安排另一架客機，接載乘客到目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5060cf127e13c01d9ba159079f6cc8351d12f730","tid":692942,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca388451ddc1a6914760cc8ab4eafbfa5803c22","tid":692942,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"咁都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ec7036f9ea2d6bfadeed855bdf7ec78025f720","tid":692942,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"月球接近近地軌道導致地球磁場嘅磁通量改變"},{"pid":"1b85e35bd1de8e88d0bbfe96ebaff4a92e28404d","tid":692942,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔使望<br />\n靠第六感降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c648a219ba63f6ae6011e4a4edc819d165bc4556","tid":692942,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"d 乘客知唔知個大銀幕打爆左<br />\n<br />\n知既話會有乜反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c76bfd235302ab7052a042307c8a5e167daeb4","tid":692942,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b85e35bd1de8e88d0bbfe96ebaff4a92e28404d","tid":692942,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔使望<br />\n靠第六感降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"有ILS，靠instrument對準跑道降落，不過好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa87b5a937cb21c2c95b3f77936e82af0bff319f","tid":692942,"uid":139873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33590795ac48baa23b421b1fb0139887c8b2fb39","tid":692942,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"諗起早排睇到 話贏國架機頭玻璃無啦啦成塊甩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dadd0fca443c067df9caa666236345811f2699c","tid":692942,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"儀錶降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}